<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='568000' id='t-568000'>So it was an early exercise</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='570000' id='t-570000'>of intellectual property rights.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:43
