<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='572000' id='t-572000'>So the thing is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573000' id='t-573000'>this kind of idea of Chinese-American food</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='576000' id='t-576000'>doesn't exist only in America.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='579000' id='t-579000'>In fact, if you think about it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='580000' id='t-580000'>Chinese food is the most pervasive food on the planet,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='582000' id='t-582000'>served on all seven continents, even Antarctica,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='585000' id='t-585000'>because Monday night is Chinese food night at McMurdo Station,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='588000' id='t-588000'>which is the main scientific station in Antarctica.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='591000' id='t-591000'>So, you see different varieties of Chinese food.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='593000' id='t-593000'>For example, there is French Chinese food,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='595000' id='t-595000'>where they serve salt and pepper frog legs.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='598000' id='t-598000'>There is Italian Chinese food,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='599000' id='t-599000'>where they don't have fortune cookies,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='602000' id='t-602000'>so they serve fried gelato.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='603000' id='t-603000'>My downstairs neighbor, Alessandra,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='604000' id='t-604000'>was completely shocked when I told her,</span>
