<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='608000' id='t-608000'>She's like, &quot;It's not?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='609000' id='t-609000'>But they serve it in all the Chinese restaurants in Italy.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='611000' id='t-611000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='616000' id='t-616000'>And even the Brits have their own version.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='618000' id='t-618000'>This is a dish called crispy shredded beef,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='620000' id='t-620000'>which has a lot of crisp, a lot of shred, and not a lot of beef.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='624000' id='t-624000'>There is West Indian Chinese food,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='626000' id='t-626000'>there's Jamaican Chinese food,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='627000' id='t-627000'>there is Middle Eastern Chinese food,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='628000' id='t-628000'>there's Mauritian Chinese food.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='630000' id='t-630000'>This is a dish called Magic Bowl</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='631000' id='t-631000'>that I discovered.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='632000' id='t-632000'>There's Indian Chinese food,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='633000' id='t-633000'>Korean Chinese food,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='635000' id='t-635000'>Japanese Chinese food,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='636000' id='t-636000'>where they take the bao, the little buns,</span>
