<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='645000' id='t-645000'>and they'll just Ramen-ize them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='646000' id='t-646000'>This is, like, this is something</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='647000' id='t-647000'>that in the Chinese version has no soup.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='649000' id='t-649000'>So, there's Peruvian Chinese food,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='651000' id='t-651000'>which should not be mixed with Mexican Chinese food,</span>
