<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='656000' id='t-656000'>And then -- one thing:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='657000' id='t-657000'>they have things like risotto chop suey.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='658000' id='t-658000'>My personal favorite</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='659000' id='t-659000'>of all the restaurants I've encountered around the world</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='663000' id='t-663000'>was this one in Brazil, called &quot;Kung Food.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='665000' id='t-665000'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
