<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='697000' id='t-697000'>but without a centralized headquarters.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698000' id='t-698000'>So, this actually became very clear to me</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='701000' id='t-701000'>with the March 30, 2005 Powerball drawing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='705000' id='t-705000'>where, you know, they expected,</span>
